'''動作摺紙'''或'''動態摺紙'''（{{lang-en|Action origami}}）<ref name="Origami_in_Action"/>是指可以設置動畫或能動的[[摺紙|摺紙]]作品，傳統的動態摺紙模式是拍動翅膀的鳥。典型動態摺紙模型總裝涉及一些特殊的動作，例如吹了一個[[紙水雷|紙水雷]]，也被歸類為'''動作摺紙'''。較少見的如沒有移動部件微調模型的[[紙飛機|紙飛機]]也都包括在內。一些傳統的動作摺紙涉及裁剪，但動態摺紙一般都沒有任何裁剪。動態摺紙通常是用來娛樂的玩具，但也有一些是設計來產生驚奇。

== 動態玩具 ==
[[File:Żaba_-_origami.jpg|thumb]]
較簡單的動態摺紙一般作為動作類玩具，包括了鳥喙在啄東西<ref name="957-6080258">{{cite book | title=《有趣的遊戲》, 摺紙作品：小雞吃米, 好玩的摺紙 | publisher=愛智圖書 | year=1992|page=P.16-17|isbn=9576080282}}</ref>、跳躍的青蛙<ref name="957-5173910">{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com.tw/books?id{{=}}XxWBMwEACAAJ&dq{{=}}isbn+9575173910&hl{{=}}zh-TW&sa{{=}}X&ei{{=}}opXlU86nOIjo8AWn1IKIBA&ved{{=}}0CBwQ6AEwAA | title=摺紙樂園 | publisher=世一文化|page=P.62-65 | author=王金芬 | year=2003|isbn=9575173910}}</ref>、或是拍動翅膀的鳥類或蝴蝶<ref name="Origami_in_Action">{{cite book|title=Origami in Action: Paper Toys that Fly, Flap, Gobble and Inflate|author=Robert J. Lang|authorlink=Robert J. Lang|isbn=0-312-15618-9|publisher=St. Martin's Griifin|year=1997}}</ref>、以及流行的傳統摺紙如[[東南西北|東南西北]]<ref name="Maguire">{{citation|title=Hopscotch, hangman, hot potato, and ha, ha, ha: a rulebook of children's games|first=Jack|last=Maguire|publisher=Simon and Schuster|year=1990|isbn=978-0-671-76332-9|pages=46–47|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=55i2ZwCYtpQC&pg=PA46|accessdate=2014-08-11|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003030015/https://books.google.com/books?id=55i2ZwCYtpQC&pg=PA46|dead-url=no}}.</ref><ref name="temkut">{{citation|title=Origami Toys|first1=Florence|last1=Temko|first2=Dave|last2=Kutchukian|publisher=Tuttle Publishing|year=2003|isbn=978-0-8048-3478-0|pages=22–23|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=c_kRTVfrhnUC&pg=PA22|accessdate=2014-08-11|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003044904/https://books.google.com/books?id=c_kRTVfrhnUC&pg=PA22|dead-url=no}}.</ref>，而[[紙鐵砲|紙鐵砲]]則是當將他往下甩時會發出爆鳴聲。

有些動作摺紙設計在摺的同時伴隨一個故事。

== 複雜的摺紙 ==
有些動態摺紙的複雜程度遠遠超過一般被歸類為玩具的動態摺紙，它們通常是要用來使人感到驚奇或震驚。比如{{link-en|羅伯特·朗|Robert J. Lang}}的《貝司手，鋼琴家，小提琴家》和是一組動作[[摺紙|摺紙]]模型，當推動它時都會有演奏樂器的動作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.langorigami.com/art/gallery/gallery.php4?name=instrumentalists|title=Bassist, Pianist, and Violinist|author=Robert J Lang|access-date=2014-08-11|archive-date=2011-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111109011109/http://langorigami.com/art/gallery/gallery.php4?name=instrumentalists|dead-url=no}}</ref>。<span class="ilh-all"><span class="ilh-page">[[:傑里米·謝弗|:傑里米·謝弗]]</span><span class="noprint ilh-comment">（<span class="ilh-lang">其他可能的</span><span class="ilh-colon">：</span><span class="ilh-link">-{Jeremy Shafer，或網路}-来源搜索：<span class="plainlinks">[//www.google.com/search?&q={{urlencode:"Jeremy Shafer"}} "Jeremy Shafer"] — [//www.google.com/search?q={{urlencode:"Jeremy Shafer"}} 网页]、[//books.google.com/books?&as_brr=0&q={{urlencode:Jeremy Shafer}} 书籍]、[//scholar.google.com/scholar?&q={{urlencode:"Jeremy Shafer"}} 学术]、[//www.google.com/search?&q={{urlencode:Jeremy Shafer}}&safe=off&tbm=isch 图像]</span></span>）</span></span>也製作了多項過人動態摺紙作品包括「使用工具打開了一把瑞士軍刀」、滑行蛇皮和閃光之物<ref name="origami_flashers" group="註">原文為origami flashers，中文名稱來源:[http://www.iqiyi.com/w_19rr4vth6t.html] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iqiyi.com/w_19rr4vth6t.html |date=20140812204034 }}、[http://v.pps.tv/play_3EQR80.html] {{Wayback|url=http://v.pps.tv/play_3EQR80.html |date=20140812212202 }}、[http://v.pps.tv/play_3EQR7Z.html] {{Wayback|url=http://v.pps.tv/play_3EQR7Z.html |date=20140812212440 }}</ref>，曾上過{{link-en|卡羅爾·杜瓦爾節目|The Carol Duvall Show}}<ref>{{cite book|title=Origami to Astonish and Amuse|url=https://archive.org/details/origamitoastonis0000shaf|author=Jeremy Shafer|authorlink=Jeremy Shafer|publisher=St. Martin's Press|isbn=0-312-25404-0|year=2001}}</ref>。

